name: Dan Wysocki's homepage
body:
Welcome to my homepage. I am an undergraduate at [SUNY Oswego](http://oswego.edu/), where I am pursuing two B.S. degrees in physics and computer science, with a minor in astronomy. I am currently working on several astronomical research projects, and wish to pursue a Ph.D in astrophysics after completing undergrad.

My resume is available [here](docs/resume.pdf).
